{
  "stem": "1753.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I took three big bottles of quinine, found some clothes, and left.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And smuggled myself out of the-- left the hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Went back to the Pawiak prison where they pick up every morning people to go into [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Kavenshein. ?] And back I went to the original place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And somehow, I nursed myself to health, by means of this medicine that I had.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So finally-- that was the total of the period that I mentioned before.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And on the 18th of July, 1943, one morning, maybe 5:00, 5:30 in the morning, the SS came charging into the camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] At that time, we were about 2,500 workers-- men, women, children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Rounded everybody up, and we had to walk to Rembertow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's near-- near a train station, maybe about five miles from the camp, and where they loaded us into the cattle cars and took us to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On a straight-- on a normal run from Rembertow to Treblinka, it probably would be two hours, maximum three hours.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think two and a half days, they ran us around, and around, and around, all over.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We finally got there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think it would have been about the 21st of July.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, we arrived in Treblinka in a sand pit, gigantic sand pit where the cattle cars came in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- but the same part of that transport was a group of Jews that worked on the Ostbahn, in the other side of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were part of that transport.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think, a total of maybe 4,000 people arrived at that pit that morning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the train arrives.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you look about you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And on the rim of that pit, the SS, and the guards, and the Ukrainians, they're all there.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
